    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>State Wide Real Estate Listing Service has been created to assist consumers in finding real estate quickly and easily. The consumer does not have to search through multiple sites to find what they are looking for. The name, State Wide Real Estate Listing Service, has been abbreviated to SWRELS.com. Several, but not all of the advantages of State Wide real Estate Listing Service include: </p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Multiple Search Options</strong><br />SWRELS.com offers the consumer four separate options to search for real estate. You can search by state, property type, textbox search or use our interactive slide show. Whichever option you decide to use you will be presented with additional search options related to your initial search.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>User Friendly</strong><br />The site has an easy to use system for consumers to navigate without having to search for properties from multiple sites.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Precise</strong><br />The site will get you to the specifics. You can choose exactly what you want to see as a consumer.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Information</strong><br />SWRELS.com will endeavor to keep consumers informed about matters of importance. Consumer participation is encouraged through the feedback link on the homepage.
        </li>
    </ul>
